	CROSS APPLY(SELECT CastedToXml.value(&#39;count(/x)&#39;,&#39;int&#39;)) B(CountOfFragments);

The idea in short:

The first `APPLY` will transform the string to a XML like this

	&lt;x&gt;H&lt;/x&gt;
